data.description: Welcome to this recently remodeled, single-story retreat in the East Mountains! Nestled on 2 fenced acres on a quiet cul-de-sac, this home offers an updated kitchen with granite counters, newer cabinetry, stainless appliances, coffee bar, breakfast nook. Renovated bathrooms with newer shower tile, bathtubs, vanities. With a host of recent upgrades including a newer furnace, evap cooler, water heater, and low-e windows, this home is truly move-in ready and primed for your comfort. Sip your morning coffee and enjoy fresh mountain air on one of two decks on either side of the home. Detached 2-car garage, additional shed, outbuildings provide endless possibilities! 2022 septic system, 2500 gal. water tank + pump. Quail Hollow recently paved/asphalted. Horses welcome!
